track_notes: Park at Ponderosa (nice cafe).  Up and over Moel y Fan then on to summit.
Short walk, stone shelter at summit.

Total time (including ops): 1hr 35m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T1. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards. Additional route information may be available at www.m1hax.uk. Track data by Richard M1HAX licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA.
track_title: Moel y Gamelin Linear from Horseshoe Pass. Aug 2020.

track_notes:
Park in large tarmac layby.

Walk back down the pass a short distance then turn right up the public footpath, then turn left to follow the narrow path parallel and above the road.

Path then goes up the cwm (dry when I went in January) towards the saddle point between the hills to join the main track up the the summit.
